9:37','2018-02-27 10:39:37'),(146,'3fd8b4ae91c18b161f41108b11d25753',9,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogcategories\\Models\\Blogcategory','{\"name\":\"News\",\"url\":\"news\",\"id\":9}','2018-03-06 09:11:09','2018-03-06 09:11:09'),(147,'455abdd4ed9af072cff2f0f85b3e5a02',46,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogs\\Models\\Blog','{\"title\":\"Very proud to be supported by The Princess Trust\",\"author\":\"\",\"url\":\"very-proud-to-be-supported-by-the-princess-trust\",\"tags\":\"Princess Trust,Charity\",\"entry\":\"<h2>Supported by the Princess Trust<\\/h2><p>We are proud to announce the support of the well known charity, The Princess Trust. Our CEO Anvay Pandya went through the Princess Trust Enterprise Programme and this is what he had to say;<\\/p><p>\\\"The Princess Trust Enterprise Programme will teach you the basics of business and provide support while you plan and launch your business. It is a must for any budding entrepreneur and I could not recommend the programme highly enough. Having the support of experienced business mentors really helps you to think critically about your business idea and what it takes to start something of your own\\\".<\\/p><p>You can take a look at the Enterprise Scheme here - <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-people\\/support-starting-business\\\">https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-pe...<\\/a> <\\/p><p>If you have any questions or would like to have a chat about the entrepreneurship or your current role within the legal field please get in touch. You can call us on 020 3633 5160 or email us at info@legalasset.co.uk.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"is_published\":\"1\",\"published_at\":\"2018-03-06 9:0:0\",\"id\":46}','2018-03-06 09:25:22','2018-03-06 09:25:22'),(148,'455abdd4ed9af072cff2f0f85b3e5a02',46,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogs\\Models\\Blog','{\"title\":\"Very proud to be supported by The Princess Trust\",\"author\":\"\",\"url\":\"very-proud-to-be-supported-by-the-princess-trust\",\"tags\":\"Princess Trust,Charity\",\"entry\":\"<h2>Supported by the Princess Trust<\\/h2><p>We are proud to announce the support of the well known charity, The Princess Trust. Our CEO Anvay Pandya went through the Princess Trust Enterprise Programme and this is what he had to say;<\\/p><p>\\\"The Princess Trust Enterprise Programme will teach you the basics of business and provide support while you plan and launch your business. It is a must for any budding entrepreneur and I could not recommend the programme highly enough. Having the support of experienced business mentors really helps you to think critically about your business idea and what it takes to start something of your own\\\".<\\/p><p>You can take a look at the Enterprise Scheme here - <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-people\\/support-starting-business\\\">https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-pe...<\\/a> <\\/p><p>If you have any questions or would like to have a chat about the entrepreneurship or your current role within the legal field please get in touch. You can call us on 020 3633 5160 or email us at info@legalasset.co.uk.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"is_published\":\"1\",\"published_at\":\"2018-03-06 9:0:0\",\"id\":46,\"image_id\":\"10\"}','2018-03-06 09:25:22','2018-03-06 09:25:22'),(149,'15d9235c9175a13be332fd7a31b0065e',46,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogs\\Models\\Blog','{\"id\":46,\"title\":\"Very proud to be supported by The Prince\'s Trust\",\"author\":\"\",\"entry\":\"<h2>Supported by the Prince\'s Trust<\\/h2><p>We are proud to announce the support of the well known charity, The Prince\'s Trust. Our CEO Anvay Pandya went through the Prince\'s Trust Enterprise Programme and this is what he had to say;<\\/p><p>\\\"The Prince\'s Trust Enterprise Programme will teach you the basics of business and provide support while you plan and launch your business. It is a must for any budding entrepreneur and I could not recommend the programme highly enough. Having the support of experienced business mentors really helps you to think critically about your business idea and what it takes to start something of your own\\\".<\\/p><p>You can take a look at the Enterprise Scheme here - <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-people\\/support-starting-business\\\">https:\\/\\/www.princes-trust.org.uk\\/help-for-young-pe...<\\/a> <\\/p><p>If you have any questions or would like to have a chat about the entrepreneurship or your current role within the legal field please get in touch. You can call us on 020 3633 5160 or email us at info@legalasset.co.uk.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"tags\":\"Princess Trust,Charity\",\"is_published\":\"1\",\"url\":\"very-proud-to-be-supported-by-the-princes-trust\",\"published_at\":\"2018-03-06 9:0:0\",\"template\":\"show\",\"image_id\":\"10\",\"seo_description\":null,\"seo_keywords\":null}','2018-03-06 10:58:51','2018-03-06 10:58:51'),(150,'64a034a061c9d4ae9f0f455042d03a78',10,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogcategories\\Models\\Blogcategory','{\"name\":\"Jobs\",\"url\":\"jobs\",\"id\":10}','2018-03-12 09:18:14','2018-03-12 09:18:14'),(151,'1a6e799fa0e207fd4ac22acc2ef9236d',47,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogs\\Models\\Blog','{\"title\":\"A fantastic role leading to training contract\",\"author\":\"\",\"url\":\"a-fantastic-role-leading-to-training-contract\",\"tags\":\"Job,Training Contract\",\"entry\":\"<h3>Legal Assistant \\/ Work Experience (Leading to Training Contract)<\\/h3><p>An excellent role has come up for a Legal Assistant through our platform. The role is with two established high street firms providing work experience and the opportunity to gain a training contract. <\\/p><ul><li>The firms are based in London in Covent Garden and Kentish Town with 2-3 days spent at each firm per week<\\/li><li>Ideally the candidate should have completed their LPC<\\/li><li>You should have an interest in Criminal and Family Law (it would help if these electives had been taken during your LPC)<\\/li><li>Some previous experience working in a law firm is required<\\/li><li>Working hours between 9am to 5.30pm (subject to the businesses needs)<\\/li><li>Reasonable expenses up to \\u00a315-20 per day until you are offered a permanent role with a training contract<\\/li><\\/ul><p>This is a great opportunity to get your foot in the door and secure a training contract with an innovative firm in a good location in the city. <\\/p><p>The role will suit a candidate who is pro-active, has critical thinking and is keen begin their legal career. As for any firm the right candidate is key and they are willing to wait for the right person.<\\/p><p>If you are interested or know someone who is please ask them to contact us at info@legalasset.co.uk or call us on 020 3633 5160.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"is_published\":\"1\",\"published_at\":\"2018-03-12 9:0:0\",\"id\":47}','2018-03-12 09:39:33','2018-03-12 09:39:33'),(152,'1a6e799fa0e207fd4ac22acc2ef9236d',47,'Quarx\\Modules\\Blogs\\Models\\Blog','{\"title\":\"A fantastic role leading to training contract\",\"author\":\"\",\"url\":\"a-fantastic-role-leading-to-training-contract\",\"tags\":\"Job,Training Contract\",\"entry\":\"<h3>Legal Assistant \\/ Work Experience (Leading to Training Contract)<\\/h3><p>An excellent role has come up for a Legal Assistant through our platform. The role is with two established high street firms providing work experience and the opportunity to gain a training contract. <\\/p><ul><li>The firms are based in London in Covent Garden and Kentish Town with 2-3 days spent at each firm per week<\\/li><li>Ideally the candidate should have completed their LPC<\\/li><li>You should have an interest in Criminal and Family Law (it would help if these electives had been taken during your LPC)<\\/li><li>Some previous experience working in a law firm is required<\\/li><li>Working hours between 9am to 5.30pm (subject to the businesses needs)<\\/li><li>Reasonable expenses up to \\u00a315-20 per day until you are offered a permanent role with a training contract<\\/li><\\/ul><p>This is a great opportunity to get your foot in the door and secure a training contract with an innovative firm in a good location in the city. <\\/p><p>The role will suit a candidate who is pro-active, has critical thinking and is keen begin their legal career. As for any firm the right candidate is key and they are willing to wait for the right person.<\\/p><p>If you are interested or know someone who is please ask them to contact us at info@legalasset.co.uk or call us on 020 3633 5160.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"is_published\":\"1\",\"published_at\":\"2018-03-12 9:0:0\",\"id\":47,\"image_id\":\"11\"}','2018-03-12 09:39:33','2018-03-12 09:39:33');
